| Range   | Purpose                |
| ------- | ---------------------- |
| 100–199 | Public inbound rules   |
| 200–299 | Private/internal rules |
| 300–399 | Outbound rules         |
| 900–999 | Explicit denies        |
--------------------------------------------

| Feature    | Security Groups    | NACLs                       |
| ---------- | ------------------ | --------------------------- |
| Level      | Instance           | Subnet                      |
| Stateful   | Yes                | No                          |
| Rules      | Allow only         | Allow & Deny                |
| Evaluation | All rules          | Rule order matters          |
| Use case   | EC2 access control | Subnet-wide traffic control |
